children.text:
Avoid roaming fees with the Tribair International SIM Card.
 When WiFi is not available, call and text in over 150 countries at low cost.
Simply insert the Tribair SIM card in any unlocked GSM phone.

Tribair SIM cards have the advantage of offering three pre-cut:
 - one standard SIM format
 - one micro SIM format (small cut)
 - one nano SIM format (very small cut)
Use WiCall Business for the best possible call quality at slightly higher call rates.
- Use Tribair to make cheap international phone calls and SMS
- Receive calls and SMS from your contacts
- Contacts don't need to use the app, they can call from any phone
